Reverb is so easy to set up 🤩

- `php artisan install:broadcasting`
- `php artisan make:event`
- Implement `ShouldBroadcast` with a channel name
- Use Echo to listen

This demo took 5 minutes to set up, and I've never seen Reverb before today. Amazing work. https://t.co/xzioqn17S0
